summary: A lightweight warm coloured ENB preset.
descriptionHtml:
I wanted a warm ENB without over-saturated greens and blues or too much bloom. The closest thing i could find is Jasmin ENB but it\'s quite old and doesn\'t support the in-game ENB menu (accessed with shift+enter). I decided to use v0.172 which support temporal anti aliasing and complex weather systems (though i haven\'t messed with the weather for now)

Credits for ENB itself of course go to Vorontsov Boris. 

Recommended downloads:
Skyrim particle patch for ENB by Mindflux: http://enbseries.enbdev.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=6&t=1499&sid=c4e8fa585f9ea0246fc5f0948df1e3d5
This fixes some issues with ENBs [fire] and [particle] settings

ENB Reference by Boris Vorontsov: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/36318/?

Required for Time of day adjustments and Temporal anti-aliasing if you want that enabled
author: 20Rakah
